~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : say                                       ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : say <message>

   This command is only needed when in COMMAND mode, since in 
   SPEECH mode everything you type that isn't a command is 
   interpreted as speech.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : shout, tell
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
